其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{E}_{2\to1}\equiv\vec{E}(\vec{r}_{1};q_{2},\vec{r}_{2})\coloneqq\frac{q_{2}}{4\mathrm{\pi}\varepsilon_{0}}\frac{\vec{r}_{1}-\vec{r}_{2}}{\vert\vec{r}_{1}-\vec{r}_{2}\vert^{3}}
\]

\end_inset

被定义为
\color red
点电荷 
\begin_inset Formula $q_{2}\mathrm{\delta}(\vec{r}-\vec{r}_{2})$
\end_inset

 在 
