\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

 内的电荷量除以 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{0}$
\end_inset

，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\oiint_{S(\vec{r})=\partial V(\vec{r})}\vec{\nu}(\vec{r})\cdot\vec{E}(\vec{r})=\iiint_{V(\vec{r}')}\frac{\rho(\vec{r}')}{\varepsilon_{0}}
\]

