\end_inset

 可视为一对电荷量为 
\begin_inset Formula $\pm Q$
\end_inset

、相对（由 
\begin_inset Formula $+Q$
\end_inset

 到 
\begin_inset Formula $-Q$
\end_inset

）位移为 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{d}$
\end_inset

 且满足 
\begin_inset Formula $Q\vec{d}=\vec{p}$
\end_inset

 的点电荷对的极限。它在 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{r}$
\end_inset

 处产生的标量势为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\phi(\vec{r}) & =\lim_{\substack{Q\to\infty\\
Q\vec{d}=\vec{p}
}
}\left(\frac{+k_{1}Q}{\vert\vec{r}-\vec{r}'-\vec{d}/2\vert}+\frac{-k_{1}Q}{\vert\vec{r}-\vec{r}'+\vec{d}/2\vert}\right)\qquad\begin{cases}
\vec{e}\coloneqq(\vec{r}-\vec{r}')/\vert\vec{r}-\vec{r}'\vert & \vert\vec{e}\vert=1\\
\vec{\epsilon}\coloneqq(\vec{d}/2)/\vert\vec{r}-\vec{r}'\vert & \vert\vec{\epsilon}\vert\ll1
\end{cases}\\
 & =\frac{k_{1}}{\vert\vec{r}-\vec{r}'\vert}\lim_{\dots}\left(\frac{Q}{\sqrt{\vec{e}\cdot\vec{e}-2\vec{e}\cdot\vec{\epsilon}+\vec{\epsilon}\cdot\vec{\epsilon}}}+\frac{-Q}{\sqrt{\vec{e}\cdot\vec{e}+2\vec{e}\cdot\vec{\epsilon}+\vec{\epsilon}\cdot\vec{\epsilon}}}\right)\\
