\begin_inset Formula $\vec{e},\vec{b}$
\end_inset

 为未知量的 Maxwell 方程组取这种空间平均，即得描述介质中的宏观电磁场的 Maxwell 方程组：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\divg\langle\vec{e}\rangle & =\langle\rho\rangle/\varepsilon_{0} & \curl\langle\vec{e}\rangle & =-\partial_{t}\langle\vec{b}\rangle\\
\divg\langle\vec{b}\rangle & =0 & \curl\langle\vec{b}\rangle & =\mu_{0}\langle\vec{\jmath}\rangle+\mu_{0}\varepsilon_{0}\partial_{t}\langle\vec{e}\rangle
\end{aligned}
\]

